org.bremersee.geojson.AbstractGeoJsonCrs

  • Packages that use AbstractGeoJsonCrs 
    Package Description
    org.bremersee.geojson
    This package contains classes for reading and writing GeoJSON with the Jackson JSON Processor.

    • Uses of AbstractGeoJsonCrs in org.bremersee.geojson

      Subclasses of AbstractGeoJsonCrs in org.bremersee.geojson 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  GeoJsonLinkedCrs
      A link to the coordinate reference system (CRS) of a GeoJSON object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#linked-crs ).
      class  GeoJsonNamedCrs
      A refernce to the coordinate reference system (CRS) of a GeoJSON object by it's name (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#named-crs ).
      Methods in org.bremersee.geojson that return AbstractGeoJsonCrs 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      AbstractGeoJsonCrs GeoJsonFeature.getCrs()
      Return the coordinate reference system (CRS) of this GeoJSON object or null if there is no such object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#coordinate-reference-system-objects ).
      AbstractGeoJsonCrs GeoJsonFeatureCollection.getCrs()
      Return the coordinate reference system (CRS) of this GeoJSON object or null if there is no such object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#coordinate-reference-system-objects ).
